org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi

Interface JdbcUserService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Documentable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JdbcUserServiceImpl

    public interface JdbcUserService
extends Documentable
    A representation of the model object 'Jdbc User Service'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Jdbc Propeties
    • Jdbc Driver
    • Authorative
    • Find User Sql
    • Find Roles For User Sql
    • Update Password Sql
    • User Id Column Name
    • Password Column Name
    • Password Type

    See Also:
    OsgiPackage.getJdbcUserService()
